snippet.title: Sonho Trap Star - Announcement Trailer | Nintendo Switch, PS4, PS5, Xbox One/Series S|X and Steam
snippet.description:
Starring Brazilian trapper DaLua, Sonho Trap Star puts players in a São Paulo overrun by zombies and a murderous militia. It offers a unique action and adventure experience inspired by the Brazilian Trap scene and the reality of the streets of São Paulo, the largest city in South America. Sonho Trap Star is coming soon to consoles and PC.
